      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It honestly breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the joy of driving a car this pristine. I\u2019ve babied this one since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape; you might find a tiny, tiny stone chip if you really go looking with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s absolutely perfect. It drives as smooth as silk and still has that fresh, clean feel inside. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and looked after, you\u2019ve found it!",
